The project has determined and developed international standards for medical devices.

Beneficiaries: Global benefit to industry and users

Contribution Method: The research resulted in a reference implementation of the standards based devices that allowed gaps to be identified and filled

Standards for smart meters.

The project can inform the policy for smart meter program in UK to incorporate the ZigBee standards in smart meter specification to support value added services.

Beneficiaries: Health

Contribution Method: The research demonstrated the value of the integrated approach based on standards to support an embedde approach to deploying monitoring solutions

ZigBee health care profile standards.

The project has determined and developed international standards for wireless medical devices based on ZigBee.

Beneficiaries: Global benefit to industry and users

Contribution Method: The research resulted in a reference implementation of the standards based devices that allowed gaps to be identified and filled

Patients were monitored.

The project monitored patients in their home and data was used by the clinician to manage their condition using an embedded solution. This may impact choice of utility providers.

Beneficiaries: Health

